{"tid":941562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日政府「中國豬瘟地圖」！沒劃入台灣","createTime":"2018-12-15T01:59:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T02:17:58.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b0fb97a2d62212d26936f6bcdef72fe030f814e5","tid":941562,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T01:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8rEzzbdG9H.PZaQUxhJ35A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mzgy/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/e905a022e1e2156e7982434e3800e0f1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F8rEzzbdG9H.PZaQUxhJ35A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mzgy%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2Fe905a022e1e2156e7982434e3800e0f1&h=62f323c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國大陸非洲豬瘟疫情擴散中，鄰近的國家皆「聞豬色變」，紛紛宣導禁帶豬肉製品入關事宜。日本政府更特別繪製「中國非洲豬瘟疫情發生狀況圖」，但值得注意的是，日本並沒有將臺灣列入中國所屬區域。<br />\n<br />\n日本政府為讓民眾了解中國非洲豬瘟疫情的擴散狀況，日本農林水產省特別製作一張「中國非洲豬瘟疫情發生狀況圖」，以中國地圖呈現，含括香港、澳門，臺灣並沒有被列入中國所屬地區，地圖中可以明顯看到疫情發源地為「黑龍江省佳木斯市」，運送1944公里到「河南省」，最終導致疫情擴散難以控制。<br />\n<br />\n地圖中的紅色「X」圖示，代表豬瘟發生地區；藍色「O」圖示代表有發生過豬瘟疫情，但已經解除封鎖的地點。根據日本統計，受感染地區共有17省、1區、4個直轄市。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B1%AC%E7%98%9F%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96-%E6%B2%92%E5%8A%83%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3-002128529.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E7%2598%259F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259C%2596-%25E6%25B2%2592%25E5%258A%2583%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3-002128529.html&d=K%2FtronHRi6BLACeVraY2JDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=5758b012\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B1%AC%E7%98%9F%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96-%E6%B2%92%E5%8A%83%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3-002128529.html</a>"},{"pid":"57e8eb571bdabdeddc0d7c7e607c70a557dcdd97","tid":941562,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:12:55.000Z","msg":"雖遠必豬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4504cb0f4cd8346799bf21864959204ce42ecb","tid":941562,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:13:40.000Z","msg":"支那豚"},{"pid":"0ab98aea4c3bb9a99f4ef0588f02029a4c7ed985","tid":941562,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:13:43.000Z","msg":"一點也不能少班撚樣出聲屌未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b287e097c73ecf8fd4c1c17faafb2801d9866fda","tid":941562,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:14:25.000Z","msg":"香港 澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"718439e4e4d9f153357e9b943824ab372966a07b","tid":941562,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ab98aea4c3bb9a99f4ef0588f02029a4c7ed985","tid":941562,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:13:43.000Z","msg":"一點也不能少班撚樣出聲屌未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:15:05.000Z","msg":"而家靠日本救命呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4921a2d15e7e3d5493cf60b7aa862c3c6f4a9a47","tid":941562,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:16:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25089fed881597127a3cacc227b0b06093b78eff","tid":941562,"uid":226622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:17:58.000Z","msg":"[打J] 如果哩張係解體後中共勢力範圍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fac